name: VentiSwap
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: VentiSwap is a non-custodial, true Cross-Chain DEX. An easy-to-use, high-efficiency experience that allows users to trade on all supported blockchains in one swap, while providing users the ability to remain fully anonymous per transaction. Other features of Venitswap include: staking, crypto news, charts and the ability to track your assets.
